<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.walkmag.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2009/03/issue_20_borders_of_history.pdf">Walking Magazine: "Borders of History"</a></li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.britain-magazine.com/features/break-for-the-borders/">Britain: "Break for the Borders"</a> Also mention of the Tironsian Abbey in Selkirk</li>
</ul>
